com.interpss.core.funcImpl

Class AclfNetObjectComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.interpss.core.funcImpl.AclfNetObjectComparator

  • public class AclfNetObjectComparator
extends java.lang.Object
    A class to compare two AclfNetwork objects, field by field, using the aclfNet1 as the base. It uses reflection to access the fields of the EMF objects and compares them.
